{"tid":2135372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地支援隊來港是否豁免檢疫　  張竹君稱沒相關資料","createTime":"2020-08-01T11:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T11:50:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bcbeb9dc2bdfefd466f8e5c3786bcf00f1fcb36a","tid":2135372,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541270-20200801.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541270-20200801.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=4b7a93e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1541270-20200801.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=392192dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1541270-20200801.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n本港連續11日單日新增過百宗新型肺炎確診個案，被問到衞生防護中心是否人手不足，衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君說，人手永遠也不夠，承認一定可以做得更好。她說，最初每日只有一兩宗個案時，追蹤工作能做得很徹底，現時已難以再用當時做法。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國家衛健委成立的首支「內地核酸檢測支援隊」其中7名成員，明日來港協助開展實驗室工作。被問到成員抵港是否豁免檢疫、工作崗位及檢測安排等，張竹君說，手上沒有詳細資料，會由政府高層公布。"},{"pid":"a039f8d3f9ffa4867b397483fb3d99564f0c3e0d","tid":2135372,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"日日都追問佢啦 次次答唔到就唔再問"},{"pid":"495c9677b6bfcc6d33602db9a2c8ab3a9f4f1bdf","tid":2135372,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a039f8d3f9ffa4867b397483fb3d99564f0c3e0d","tid":2135372,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:32:43.000Z","msg":"日日都追問佢啦 次次答唔到就唔再問"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:43:11.000Z","msg":"唔追問：何時會有補充資料？ 一個鐘後會否發補充資料？<br />\n<br />\n香港妓者根本係垃圾中既廢物"},{"pid":"619755bfb00fb52186430d7e4fb30e09ba32125f","tid":2135372,"uid":355748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"點解你咩都冇資料<br />\n你有咩存在價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32421700e46e0523878ac6da08e61aa122aac94b","tid":2135372,"uid":353629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T11:50:26.000Z","msg":"到底黎救人定黎害人"}]}